  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    se.sics.jasper.SPTerm.consFunctor(String, int, SPTerm[])

    Use putCanonicalAtom instead.
    se.sics.jasper.SICStus.query(SPPredicate, SPTerm[])
    Use module and predicate name directly instead (SICStus.query(String, String, SPTerm[])).
    se.sics.jasper.SICStus.queryCutFail(SPPredicate, SPTerm[])
    Use module and predicate name directly instead (SICStus.queryCutFail(String, String, SPTerm[])).
  • Deprecated Constructors
